summary: Quantum computing technology is at an inflection point, Nvidia (NVDA) CEO Jensen Huang told the VivaTech conference in Paris on Wednesday, adding that quantum computing will solve “some interesting problems” in the coming years, Reuters’ Supantha Mukherjee reported.
